Buffton Corp said it completedthe purchase of B and D Industruments Inc for two mln dlrs cashand 400,000 shares of common stock.    It said B and D is a private company headquartered inKansas, and had sales of 4,700,000 dlrs in 1986.    Buffton said the company designs and manufactures aviationcomputer display systems and engine instrumentation. Reuter&#3;